<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT36">
<l>nākat taṇaikkuṭantai veḵkā tiruvevvuḷ</l>
<l>nākat taṇaiyaraṅkam pēraṉpil nākat</l>
<l>taṇaippāṟ kaṭalkiṭakku māti neṭumā</l>
<l>laṇaippār karuttaṉā vāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On the snake bed in Kuṭantai, Veḵkā, [and] the sacred Evvuḷ,</l>
<l>On the snake bed in Raṅgam, Pēr, [and] Aṉpil,</l>
<l>on the snake bed on the milky ocean</l>
<l rend="indent">lies the primordial tall Māl</l>
<l>[in order] to be in the minds of those who embrace [Him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
